																		I think this might be the shortest tale I&#039;ve written...
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610225122" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;" >Jacob Conwell</a></span> <span class="odate time_1503265923 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">20 Aug 2017 21:52</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3574850">
									

<p>Alright, so I must be in an epilogue kind of mood, because, since <a href="/scp-3560">SCP-3560</a> is now a thing, this serves as a bit of closure on the relationship Researcher Conwell and <a href="/scp-1360">SCP-1360</a> had in the <a href="/peregrine">Peregrine</a> series of tales.</p>
<p>Its short, but I like the characterization the previously muted SCP-1360 gets here.</p>
<p>Special thanks to the following for their critiques: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053945" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;">Taffeta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/salvagebar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1479603); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1479603&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053945" alt="salvagebar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1479603)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/salvagebar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1479603); return false;">salvagebar</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053945" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053945" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3129691); return false;">Modern_Erasmus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053945" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(560062); return false;">minmin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2887044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2887044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053945" alt="DrBleep" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2887044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drbleep" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2887044); return false;">DrBleep</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2527320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1504053945" alt="LordStonefish" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2527320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lordstonefish" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2527320); return false;">LordStonefish</a></span></p>
<p>Enjoy the tale.</p>
<p>JC</p>

