			<div class="content" id="post-content-3576426">
									

<p>Fair enough.</p>
<p>I'd argue that on top of being a robot, Hector's also been isolated from that family for the better part of two and half (or so) decades by the time this tale roles around, which leaves along time for things to kind of fade and become distant through reflection, hence Hector's coldness.</p>

